OL,3,CGovernment publishes flagship welfare
OL,4,Creforms as Labour rebellion looms
OL,6,FLiz Kendall's words come amid a
OL,7,Fbacklash from some Labour MPs who have
OL,8,Fcriticised the "awful" cuts to welfare
OL,9,F` which the government hopes can save
OL,10,Fup to #5 billion a year.
OL,12,FThe reforms ` aimed at encouraging
OL,13,Fmore people off sickness benefits and
OL,14,Finto work ` are set to include the
OL,15,Ftightening of criteria for personal
OL,16,Findependence payment (Pip), which is
OL,17,Fthe main disability benefit, as well
OL,18,Fas a cut to the sickness-related
OL,19,Felement of universal credit (UC) and
OL,20,Fdelayed access to only those aged 22
OL,21,Fand over.
