OL,6,FMinisters are likely to face a Commons
OL,7,Fstand-off with backbench Labour MPs
OL,8,Fover their plans, with dozens of them
OL,9,Flast month saying the proposals were
OL,10,F"impossible to support".
OL,12,FIn what could be seen as an attempt to
OL,13,Fhead off some opposition, the
OL,14,Flegislation, known as the Universal
OL,15,FCredit and Personal Independence
OL,16,FPayment Bill ` will give existing
OL,17,Fclaimants a 13-week period of
OL,18,Ffinancial support.
