OL,15,Falongside Wednesday's Bill
OL,16,Fintroduction, confirmed previously
OL,17,Fpublished estimates that changes to
OL,18,FPip entitlement rules could see about
OL,19,F800,000 people lose out, with an
OL,20,Faverage loss of #4,500 per year.
